high_descs: Move to the white fridge in the corner of the room
Open the fridge and remove the dirty mug from the fridge
Carry the mug over to the sink
Wash the mug in the sink then remove it
Carry the mug to the blue coffee maker on top of the counter
Place the mug under the coffee maker on the counter
anns.task_desc: Clean a mug to place on the coffee maker

high_descs: move to the fridge to the right of the coffee maker
pick up a mug from the fridge
move to the sink to the left
clean the mug in the sink
move to the coffee maker to the left of the fridge
put the mug on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned mug on the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk to the front of the fridge.
Open the fridge door, take out a cup from the second shelf, close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk to the kitchen sink.
Place the mug inside of the sink and to the left of the egg, turn the water on and rinse off the mug, turn the water off, pick up the mug from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the counter to the left of the fridge with the coffee maker on it.
Place the mug in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: To rinse off a mug and place it in the coffee maker.
